                        "content": "During an admission assessment, the nurse notes that the client's diagnosis is documented as obsessive-compulsive disorder. The nurse plans care, knowing that the client is most likely to experience which type of compulsive behavior?",
                        "subjectId": "ad5ab04c79144c0ea9b83385308c3b1d",
                        "difficultyIds": "80db17ea97ed8fdcd1b6b9666390fca1",
                        "difficulty": "考试范围-Applying 应用",
                        "textAnalysis": "Rationale:\nA compulsion is a repetitive act. The client with a phobia is likely to experience unreasonable fears. Illusions are characterized by misinterpretation of events. An obsession is a repetitive thought.\n\nClient Needs: Psychosocial Integrity\nClinical Judgment/Cognitive Skill(s): Generate Solutions\nCognitive Ability: Applying\nContent Area: Mental Health\nHealth Problem: Mental Health: Obsessive-Compulsive Disorder\nIntegrated Process: Nursing Process/Planning\nPriority Concepts: Anxiety, Mood and Affect\nStrategies: Strategic Words, Subject\n\nTest-Taking Strategy:\nFocus on the subject, compulsive behavior. Also note the strategic words, most likely. Recalling the definition of a compulsion and that a compulsion is an act will direct you to the correct option.\n ",
                        "id": "35602008299b44a9bde388df0bc0a219",
                        "mark": "0",
                        "collectionState": "0"
                    },
                    {
                        "optionList": [
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "5efa87342c33474aaae422c9adfa310b",
                                "content": "\"Inner voices tell me to perform my rituals.\""
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "66ac4e4990264735826a98fe55976df2",
                                "content": "\"My behavior is a conscious attempt to punish myself.\""
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "5b73552c4d3a46f7ba87c21a1dd697e3",
                                "content": "\"I'm demonstrating control when I engage in my rituals.\""
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "1",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "2b7b7fcd76824355b4d62bb4eff544a4",
                                "content": "\"My rituals are ways for me to control unpleasant thoughts or feelings.\""
                            }
